                    "title": "Reset Board 1",
                    "transmitFunction": "/**\n * Clear stored calibration on TB board 1 — command 1.\n *\n * Command ID (type=2, board=1, cmd=1) = 0x609, DLC 0. Erases the stored\n * record and reverts the live trims to the build-time defaults.\n */\nfunction transmit(value) {\n  return canSendFrame(0x609, []);\n}\n"
