                    "transmitFunction": "/**\n * Clear stored calibration on TB board 5 — command 1.\n *\n * Command ID (type=2, board=5, cmd=1) = 0x629, DLC 0. Erases the stored\n * record and reverts the live trims to the build-time defaults.\n */\nfunction transmit(value) {\n  return canSendFrame(0x629, []);\n}\n"
